<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>The Garden is a Loop</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  <style>
    /* Inline styles moved to main.css */
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="background"></div>

    <img src="/2dassets/title1.png" alt="Title Part 1" class="title-image title-image-left">
    <img src="/2dassets/title2.png" alt="Title Part 2" class="title-image title-image-right">
    <p class="tiny-text">whispers of sound in a visual space</p>
    <div class="hidden-nav">
      <div class="nav-item" id="create-garden">Create New Garden</div>
      <a href="/explore" class="nav-item">Explore Gardens</a>
    </div>
    <!-- Introduction text replacing the garden gallery -->
    <div class="intro-text">
      <p>Here, music is planted, not played.</p>
      <p>Each plant defines a sound.</p>
      <p>Time grows in space, and melodies weave themselves.</p>
    </div>
  
  <div class="overlay" id="overlay"></div>
  
  <div id="create-form" class="form-container">
    <div class="close-btn">&times;</div>
    <h2 class="form-title">New Garden</h2>
    <form action="/saveGarden" method="POST">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="owner">Your Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="owner" name="owner" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="gardenName">Garden Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="gardenName" name="gardenName" required>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn">Create Garden</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
